title: 14/10/2015 Leanne Wood warns of Wales Bill “race to the bottom” (Party of Wales)
text: ( Source : Party of Wales ) NEWS RSS 14/10/ 2015 Plaid Cymru will not accept weak Wales Bill Plaid Cymru leader Leanne Wood has warned that her party will not accept a weak Wales Bill, that doesn't give Wales a distinct legal jurisdiction.
